flowchart TB
    classDef user fill:#eaf3ff,stroke:#2b5c99,color:#1d2d3f
    classDef process fill:#e7f6ec,stroke:#2f855a,color:#1d2d3f
    classDef runtime fill:#eee8ff,stroke:#6b46c1,color:#1d2d3f
    classDef slurm fill:#fff2df,stroke:#b96c00,color:#1d2d3f
    classDef external fill:#ffe5e8,stroke:#c53030,color:#1d2d3f
    classDef product fill:#eaf8f0,stroke:#2f855a,color:#1d2d3f

    scientist["Scientist or developer"]
    parset["Parset runtime options"]
    rapthor_proc["Rapthor process"]

    subgraph local_no_server["Local no-server mode"]
        ephemeral_prefect["Ephemeral/local Prefect state"]
        local_dask["Local Dask scheduler and workers"]
    end

    subgraph persistent_dashboard["Optional persistent dashboard mode"]
        prefect_api["Prefect API"]
        prefect_dashboard["Prefect dashboard"]
    end

    subgraph external_dask["Optional external Dask mode"]
        dask_scheduler["Dask scheduler"]
        dask_workers["Dask workers"]
        dask_dashboard["Dask dashboard"]
    end

    subgraph slurm_allocation["Production-style Slurm allocation"]
        slurm_job["Slurm job"]
        worker_nodes["Allocated nodes"]
        mpi_wsclean["WSClean MPI ranks"]
        node_tools["DP3, WSClean, LoSoTo, fpack, PyBDSF"]
    end

    products["Working directory, logs, profiles, products"]
    browser["Local browser via direct access or SSH tunnels"]

    scientist -->|runs rapthor input.parset| rapthor_proc
    scientist -->|edits| parset
    parset -->|selects runtime shape| rapthor_proc

    rapthor_proc -->|default when no PREFECT_API_URL| ephemeral_prefect
    rapthor_proc -->|default local execution| local_dask

    rapthor_proc -->|reports state when configured| prefect_api
    prefect_api -->|serves| prefect_dashboard
    browser -->|opens| prefect_dashboard

    rapthor_proc -->|connects when configured| dask_scheduler
    dask_scheduler -->|schedules tasks| dask_workers
    dask_scheduler -->|serves| dask_dashboard
    browser -->|opens| dask_dashboard

    rapthor_proc -->|submitted by| slurm_job
    slurm_job -->|allocates| worker_nodes
    worker_nodes -->|host| dask_workers
    worker_nodes -->|launch| mpi_wsclean
    worker_nodes -->|run| node_tools

    local_dask -->|write| products
    dask_workers -->|write| products
    mpi_wsclean -->|write images| products
    node_tools -->|write command outputs| products
    rapthor_proc -->|write run metadata| products

    class scientist,browser,parset user
    class rapthor_proc process
    class ephemeral_prefect,local_dask,prefect_api,prefect_dashboard,dask_scheduler,dask_workers,dask_dashboard runtime
    class slurm_job,worker_nodes,mpi_wsclean slurm
    class node_tools external
    class products product
